exterior view in Silicon Valley. - Palo Alto, California, USA - 2019\" data-id=\"1313497441\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5564px\" height=\"3746px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Michael Vi</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Co-Authored by Noah Cox and Brock Heilig</em></p> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Palantir Technologies (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PLTR\" title=\"Palantir Technologies Inc.\">PLTR</a></span>) shares have beaten the market since the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4734158-palantir-q3-earnings-deep-dive-after-the-election\">last time</a> I wrote on them (November 7th) after the US Presidential election and the most recent earnings</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745736-palantir-winning-the-race-to-agi", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 08:52:32", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745735", "title": "Wix.com: Full Steam Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"video hosting website. movie streaming service. digital photo album.\" data-id=\"861148402\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">metamorworks</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>With the S&amp;P 500 continuing to straddle all-time highs amid growing valuation concerns and the prospect that the Fed may slow down the pace of rate decreases, it has been more critical than ever to pivot our portfolios toward \"growth</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745735-wixcom-full-steam-ahead-wix-stock", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 08:35:08", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745734", "title": "Children's Place Is Highly Volatile But Still Represents A Speculative Buy", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1869089642/image_1869089642.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Portrait of smiling boy and girl standing with arm around\" data-id=\"1869089642\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1869089642/image_1869089642.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1869089642/image_1869089642.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1869089642/image_1869089642.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1869089642/image_1869089642.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1869089642/image_1869089642.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1869089642/image_1869089642.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1869089642/image_1869089642.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1869089642/image_1869089642.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Children's Place (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PLCE\" title=\"The Children's Place, Inc.\">PLCE</a></span>) has recently experienced many corporate developments. The company released disappointing 3Q24 results, followed by improvements for November and December 2024, plus the pricing of its rights offering.</p> <p>We will cover those developments in this article and revisit</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1869089642/image_1869089642.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745734-childrens-place-is-highly-volatile-but-still-represents-a-speculative-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 08:30:29", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745743", "title": "Key Charts That Defined Markets And The Economy In 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Calculator and charts\" data-id=\"160616076\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"3648px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w480